            <thetext>As a demo implementation, Feedreader should be created with separate I18N parts 
(config packages/i18n-with-boot:false). But this also requires that these parts 
have to be loaded by the Feedreader class code at appropriate times:

- the initial language part has to be loaded once the current locale is known
- other i18n parts have to be loaded when the user choses another language from 
the &quot;Preferences&quot; dialog.</thetext>
